data.description: Welcome to 7306 Eton Drive in Rowlett, Texas! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is a haven of comfort and style. Recently updated with stunning luxury vinyl plank flooring and fresh paint, the interior radiates modern elegance. The home boasts recent upgrades to key systems, including HVAC, water heater, and fence, ensuring peace of mind for the lucky new owners. Nestled in the highly desirable Garland ISD, it offers the flexibility to choose from a range of excellent schools within the district. With a spacious lot exceeding a quarter of an acre, this property invites you to embrace a lifestyle of tranquility and room to roam. Don't miss the chance to make 7306 Eton Drive your new home sweet home!
